&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the Enterprise Applications CRM and ERP teams to ensure alignment across platforms and maintain architectural integrity across the full enterprise application ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Information Security and IT Operations to ensure integrations meet security, compliance, infrastructure, and operational standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with business partners including FSDA in Development, FP&amp;amp;A, and Finance to ensure integrations support accurate data flows, operational needs, and long term business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
