&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with business and technical stakeholders to validate integration requirements, ensuring accuracy, feasibility, and alignment with HRW’s SDLC standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate functional needs into scalable technical integration designs, including data mapping, API usage, orchestration flows, and system interdependencies.&lt;/li&gt;
