&lt;li&gt;Write and publicize reports, briefing papers, letters, news releases, op-eds, and submissions to international bodies; collect supporting documents and materials such as photographs and videos;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the development and implementation of local, regional, and international strategies to change abusive laws, policies, and practices;&lt;/li&gt;
