&lt;li&gt;Lead development and implementation of local, regional, and international strategies to change abusive laws, policies, and practices in Myanmar;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to queries from the media, public, and colleagues in the human rights community and take initiative to project concerns in public debates;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Place abuses within the broader political, social and economic contexts and present human rights concerns to government officials, opinion leaders, inter-governmental agencies, and the media;&lt;/li&gt;
