&lt;li&gt;Lead internal HRW policy discussions on issues relevant to their work;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make recommendations to the US Program regarding the strategic research and advocacy projects it should prioritize regarding criminal justice, and develop and lead on those projects;&lt;/li&gt;
